  <!-- EN: walker frame -->
  <WG_HeavyExoskeleton.label>步行框架</WG_HeavyExoskeleton.label>
  <!-- EN: A primitive and bulky heavy-duty exoskeleton. Although such large wearable exoskeletons have been repeatedly invented since the 22nd century, their design and technical foundations are interoperable.\n\nThe application environment of powered frames in the military is close to small mechas or some genetically modified large humanoid soldiers. Still, its degree of automation is low and requires pilot to use full body control, and relies on a specialized maintenance platform to put on and take off. -->
  <WG_HeavyExoskeleton.description>一種原始且笨重的大型外骨骼。雖然這種大型穿戴式外骨骼自22世紀以來便不斷的被重複發明，但大體上的設計和技術基礎都能夠互通。 \n\n步行框架在軍隊中的應用環境接近小型機甲或一些基因改造大型人形士兵。但其自動化程度較低，需要駕駛員全身控制並依靠專門的維修平台進行登機與整備。</WG_HeavyExoskeleton.description>
